        public java.io.InputStream downloadFile(UriComponents uriComponents)
        Description copied from interface: DownloadService
        Downloads a file using the parameters within the UriComponents.

        Rather than passing the full url to the function, the details are separated so the URI can parse the special characters in the path properly.

        Specified by:
        downloadFile in interface DownloadService
        Parameters:
        uriComponents - component that has all the details to download a file
        Returns:
        null or an InputStream based on whether the download was successful or not
